{"tid":1404451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你Ｄ差佬閃撚夠未，我朋友阿媽爭D俾你地閃到要CALL白車","createTime":"2019-08-04T04:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T10:17:01.000Z","uid":70786,"like":355,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"5bbb252dbea977616d3826d86f6f5a0efa6fe755","tid":1404451,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/533354893870793/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F533354893870793%2F&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USHO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=9010a19e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/533354893870793/</a><br />\n我朋友住黃大仙，尋日咁大件事佢就叫咗兩老起身睇新聞直播<br />\n其中黃大仙現場報導有大量警察用強烈閃光照射在場人士及鏡頭<br />\n佢阿媽睇睇睇下突然感到不適，面同手有輕微抽搐同痺痛<br />\n我朋友立即叫佢阿媽瞓梳化同熄電視<br />\n休息咗大概20分鐘先恢復正常<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">警察公共關係科高級警尸余鎧均對於有記者多次被警方以強光照射干擾拍攝，余鎧均稱燈可以用作照明，又或是辨別激進示威者的身份，由於當時場面相當混亂，開燈的原因最終要問現場的警員。</span><br />\n<br />\n閃到好似去concert咁都叫照明用途？我屌你老母啦<br />\n希望醫護界及香港協癇會可以出嚟譴責有關行為！"},{"pid":"3293203f34aba07f63628178eb1dffb41ff90dd8","tid":1404451,"uid":265256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a14568488d57c8f3c6241e1dbd60a01d0c4daa","tid":1404451,"uid":168381,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"癲癇發作"},{"pid":"05363beef1ecaacf7f8afbc600bdb31b107f0166","tid":1404451,"uid":45007,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"諗起當年比卡超事件"},{"pid":"f1b8ac4ee749d6d31cdd00c1f02b2bf5def93b28","tid":1404451,"uid":70786,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"49a14568488d57c8f3c6241e1dbd60a01d0c4daa","tid":1404451,"uid":168381,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"癲癇發作"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201