uid":76680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:00:24.000Z","msg":"直接攞反光板照返佢地得唔得?<br />\n應該就算記者用反光板,都應該得?<br />\nPPRB都講到明係為拍攝就可以"},{"pid":"bb2ed97fbe9a865db330448e4279403ed15ee661","tid":1404451,"uid":189875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05363beef1ecaacf7f8afbc600bdb31b107f0166","tid":1404451,"uid":45007,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"諗起當年比卡超事件"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:01:48.000Z","msg":"當年好多小朋友出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a1f1570e09a3045769277db30fd261fbc48ab3","tid":1404451,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c32ea739b058346362ab6505c11223656a966d5","tid":1404451,"uid":76680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:00:24.000Z","msg":"直接攞反光板照返佢地得唔得?<br />\n應該就算記者用反光板,都應該得?<br />\nPPRB都講到明係為拍攝就可以"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"反光板都唔夠佢直射咁強<br />\nD狗真係癲撚咗"},{"pid":"280eec78f8c5f046739e6b5a3e354bc08b60550a","tid":1404451,"uid":76680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c3a1f1570e09a3045769277db30fd261fbc48ab3","tid":1404451,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c32ea739b058346362ab6505c11223656a966d5","tid":1404451,"uid":76680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:00:24.000Z","msg":"直接攞反光板照返佢地得唔得?<br />\n應該就算記者用反光板,都應該得?<br />\nPPRB都講到明係為拍攝就可以"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"反光板都唔夠佢直射咁強<br />\nD狗真係癲撚咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:11:39.000Z","msg":"我意思係反一反D光,比D狗都曬下燈,<br />\n當然唔係為左硬碰硬,<br />\n硬碰硬梗係鬥照光"},{"pid":"9c100e61590c35f7b301dc0bad36d2524a90459a","tid":1404451,"uid":261505,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"其實閃燈有機會引發癲癇發作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6376cdf644